<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Order Expired</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>Unfortunately, your order <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> has expired because the payment was not completed within the given time limit.</p>
    <p>If you still wish to attend the event, please create a new order.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><strong>Ticketing Team</strong></p>
</body>
</html>
